。再说下去没有任何意义，后来我也不去找别人发牢骚了。 但是那些让我焦虑的社交场合到处都是，怎么做才能缓解？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-ae209820263b0f0bb345a3679ad83cf5_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "18 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/661086933"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI9Mm06p3fyIwPEAMaCTEwOTE4NTc5NCDa/K+0BjAAOIICQCVyCTY2MTA4NjkzM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1720576561.44434", "card_id": "Q_660083375", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 45}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《红楼梦》的作者可能会是书中的谁？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如果作者就是书中的某一人物，大家觉得会是谁呢？ 作者作为一个观察者，极大可能会把自己也写进书里，他的位置，在哪里呢？ 有点儿创意当然最好。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-558541bdff633b8d29df2871025dc649_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "18 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660083375"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9Mm06p3fyIwPEAMaCTEwODk2MzA5MSCD2/SzBjAAOExAJnIJNjYwMDgzMzc1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1720576561.44871", "card_id": "Q_660424819", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 49}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么有了 CPU，还要研究 GPU？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "为什么有了 CPU，还要研究 GPU，二者有什么区别？芯片还会往什么方向发展？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-04f61f566fc817687ef90883648e97ac_r.jpg?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "18 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660424819"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI9Mm06p3fyIwPEAMaCTEwOTAzODg2OCDrtYi0BjAAOO8BQCdyCTY2MDQyNDgxOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type